<function>

access:   public

name: addValid

param: string, $name

param: string, $method

param: string, $message, NULL

return: void

</function>

Adds a Solar_Valid method callback as a validation for an element.

* Parameters:

 * string //$name//: The element name.

 * string //$method//: The Solar_Valid callback method.

 * string //$message//: The message to use if validation fails.

* Returns void

Adds a Solar_Valid method callback as a validation for an element.